Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.58,0:00:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My head!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.16,0:00:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My head is splitting open!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.08,0:00:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a new form of attack \Nby the dark alliance?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.42,0:00:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to get the regular size.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.92,0:00:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I award you the privilege to enjoy half.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.51,0:00:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.89,0:00:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, our day alone together began.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.89,0:00:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our one, precious day together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.23,0:02:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why doesn't he have his dog with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:09.22,Copy of Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Triangle...\Nof Missed Encounters
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.38,0:02:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Saigo doesn't come\Nwith his dog in Kagoshima.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.24,0:02:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come? This is Mr. Saigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.78,0:02:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone knows Mr. Saigo comes with a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.04,0:02:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see what all the fuss is about...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.91,0:02:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but let's go look at another Mr. Saigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.26,0:02:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there's a dog way \Nover there! There's a dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm taking the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.34,0:02:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say "cheese."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.51,0:02:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.55,0:02:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got separated from my group.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you last see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.22,0:02:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the souvenir shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.81,0:02:36.92,Copy of Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try calling them on your cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's finally awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:38.63,Copy of Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.90,0:02:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? I'm on after-exam vacation.\NWhy are you calling so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.83,0:02:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get my voice mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not go and use my voice mail system\Nwithout permission...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.78,0:02:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...fake magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.53,0:02:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, be quiet! Never mind, and just delete it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.33,0:02:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delete what? Your existence on this Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.35,0:02:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that page on the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you're the one who went and made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you blithering about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because you're getting fat\Nis no reason to take it out on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.57,0:03:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking gibberish!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't talk your way out of this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now listen. That page better be gone\Nby the time I get back...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.43,0:03:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or I'll force a gallon \Nof milk down your throat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That faker finally returns my call,\Nand she's full of nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she was lonely\Nfor the sound of my voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe she was going to ask me\Nhow I was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Internet page?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.58,0:03:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is amazing from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're so close to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.37,0:03:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resonating frequency perceived\Nat a radius of five kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.21,0:03:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical beings detected\Nnear the vicinity of the crater.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be the red dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed how easily you\Ncome up with those delusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.09,0:03:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta, I fear that the dragon's body\Nhas shattered through the crater.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may have split into seven parts.\NWe need to collect them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.14,0:03:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna cross over to the other side?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cross? Can we get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.02,0:04:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I think we can take a boat across.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Schwartz Schneesturm!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Schneeglöckchen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.42,0:04:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt it's anything like\Nwhatever you're imagining.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we have plenty of time,\Nand it won't take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.89,0:04:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-hey, you're Shichimiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.81,0:04:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero, it's you! Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry! I never expected to\Nfind him in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.82,0:04:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You took the words out of my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you also on a school field trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.78,0:04:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.03,0:04:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are indeed the Hero with whom\NI once trusted my fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked Lord Shingan. I'm sorry.\NI apologize for grabbing on to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so startled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is far too late for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical devil girl, Sophia \NRing SP Saturn VII!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are now treading upon the territory...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...within my Wicked Lord's dark barrier\Nin which I cannot be defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna make war?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.68,0:05:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're alone together, are you?\NThen I will let you go this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.56,0:05:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sophia Ring has been tasked\Nwith an angel-finding mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.49,0:05:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wander off that way. Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.78,0:05:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to ask, but can I borrow 500 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm revived!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you come so far\Nonly to misplace your bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,0:05:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The angel may be running interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.01,0:05:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are large shockwaves\Ncoming from Area Zero to the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:05:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you make it back to your hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.39,0:06:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never fear! I have memorized every route!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have a clue\Nwhich way to go, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it. Is your cell \Nphone also in the bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.44,0:06:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.44,0:06:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine. The whole \Nworld is linked together...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so all roads lead to \Nwhere they need to lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.00,0:06:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can make it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.12,0:06:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never go near any girl but you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.26,0:06:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this and begone\Nto wherever you choose to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't solve it with money!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.51,0:06:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.76,0:06:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rikka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.60,0:06:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will soon locate it with\Nthe power of Wicked Lord Shingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.56,0:06:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.06,0:06:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.73,0:06:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.69,0:06:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I found\Na piece of paper inside my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:06:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:00.56,Copy of Default,,0000,0000,0000,,THE WHISPERS OF\NMORI SUMMER
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.74,0:07:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.58,0:07:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.08,0:07:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fake Mori Summer, how do you dare\Nuse the name of Mori Summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.09,0:07:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? You're the one\Nwho made that page, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have never seen this page before!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made it because you are the fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.13,0:07:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? I would never make such a thing,\Nand you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then who made it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're asking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.81,0:07:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be the true one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You walked through here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.36,0:07:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was tracking the angel's signature.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.49,0:07:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember taking\Nanything out of your bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.24,0:07:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got on and off the train with my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bought some candy and we split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.87,0:07:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I walked through here eating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.12,0:07:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you would have had the bag\Nwhen you were in the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.13,0:08:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A spirit tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.68,0:08:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is big.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must have incredible magical powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.89,0:08:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two agree about the weirdest things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichimiya, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it! Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You're good, Wicked Lord Shingan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is to be expected with\Nthe power of Wicked Lord Shingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's a monkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dark follower!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, that's a monkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of the\NWicked Lord Shingan can handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.67,0:08:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can easily obliterate an ape being or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.96,0:08:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it. It'll bite you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.97,0:08:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to drive it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that could make it attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.64,0:08:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.73,0:08:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.81,0:08:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichimiya, do you remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the split-second formation - revised?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Split-second? Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.53,0:09:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka, you stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.78,0:09:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Split-second Formation - revised!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.09,0:09:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.64,0:09:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichimiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.14,0:09:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.02,0:09:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichimiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:09:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We're rusty, but we pulled off\Nthe split-second formation - revised!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.42,0:10:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I haven't tried that since.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you'd actually remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.89,0:10:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have decided to remain\Nunchanged for all eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.10,0:10:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Along with the magical power\NI cultivated with you back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.81,0:10:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the missions I was awarded\Nas a magical devil girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite the weirdo yourself, Shichimiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not weird. I won't change, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.41,0:10:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.03,0:10:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? An arcade token?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.58,0:10:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your memories have already\Nbeen taken from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.04,0:10:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta? Yuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.34,0:10:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Thanks, Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.22,0:10:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Rikka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:10:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:11:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta, you have forgotten your contract!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.44,0:11:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka? Hey, Rikka!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.40,0:11:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked Lord Shingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.58,0:11:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Mr. Saigo doesn't have a dog either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.25,0:11:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Saigo doesn't have his dog with him\Nhere in Kagoshima.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.81,0:11:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.01,0:11:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Takanashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did she go? I hope she didn't get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She isn't answering her phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. This is 100% my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I butted in on your private time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.49,0:11:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so wrapped up in the bag hunt,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.35,0:11:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NI didn't stop to consider her feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.62,0:12:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I want you to head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:04.62,Copy of Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prefectural Citizens\NExchange Centre
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.21,0:12:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, really. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.67,0:12:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your school field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, there's a bus stop right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can find your way back\Nif you get to a station.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.43,0:12:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.64,0:12:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it. Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oof.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.78,0:12:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to lose some weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.38,0:12:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Togashi residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.17,0:12:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Shichimiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.25,0:12:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Satone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I need info quick, if you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:54.04,Copy of Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bus Stop
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh. Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:12:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.94,0:13:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Shichimiya and Togashi were with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.23,0:13:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.65,0:13:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means they were goofing around\Ntogether and neglecting you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.57,0:13:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you were all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was alone because I broke away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is Togashi doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:36.92,Copy of Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Received Mail
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:38.17,Copy of Default,,0000,0000,0000,,RECEIVED MAIL\NIT'S SOPHIA
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.81,0:13:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Map.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.08,0:13:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got a map?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You ran into Rikka?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Togashi, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.32,0:13:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you know that\Npaying attention to Shichimiya
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.49,0:14:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while you're spending time alone\Nwith Rikka will upset her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. Do you know where she went?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.66,0:14:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She glanced at a map and dashed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.54,0:14:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. It's okay, I'll take care of it. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.26,0:14:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again? Kuzuha?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:14.41,Copy of Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incoming Call\NHome
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.97,0:14:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making you come all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax, I came alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one will get in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.45,0:14:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will give you fair warning.\NWicked Lord Shingan is all powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the most supreme level of light's\Nmagical power cannot defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.92,0:14:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit while you still can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.59,0:14:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The manifestation of his physical speed\Nin this world is equally great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:14:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To fully observe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.31,0:15:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.48,0:15:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then find out to your peril just how powerful\Nthe magical devil girl really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which would be fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I didn't ask you \Nto come here to make war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.79,0:15:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted you to hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.88,0:15:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought maybe I gave you\Nthe wrong idea about Hero and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta, not Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.42,0:15:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero is what I've always called him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.05,0:15:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so he will always be a hero to me.\NGrant me that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.64,0:15:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. So anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you and Hero are bound by the\NLover's Contract, right, Wicked Lord Shingan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:15:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's it to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.03,0:16:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like that once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once, I also felt my heart flutter\Nwhen I thought about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.66,0:16:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I wanted to always be with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.25,0:16:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But once that happened,\Nall sorts of things began to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.13,0:16:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is definitely the \Nsignature of a magical being.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.30,0:16:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.39,0:16:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Sophia?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another inter-dimensional quake\Nthrough the alternate world line?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could feel my powers gradually ebbing away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.99,0:16:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.62,0:16:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I started to think that maybe\NI wasn't a magical devil girl after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt it gradually lose its meaning for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.73,0:17:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.68,0:17:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.49,0:17:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided that I would stay\Njust the way I was, forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.25,0:17:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In accordance to the logic of\Nthe world and its natural laws...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.42,0:17:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I decided to stay as I was,\Nas a magical devil girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am magical devil girl,\NSophia Ring SP Saturn VII!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will forsake all else to live my life\Nto the fullest with my powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.85,0:17:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying that Hero's partner is you,\NWicked Lord Shingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will not change.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Wicked Lord Shingan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.90,0:18:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to stay the\NWicked Lord Shingan forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.66,0:18:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think you can revive\Nthe Dark Flame Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you give him that token?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.37,0:18:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I originally owned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think Hero\Neven remembers that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although it isn't my place to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have an angel to track down,\Nso I'm gone! Zoom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.68,0:18:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sophia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.94,0:18:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.66,0:18:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Shichimiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.99,0:18:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that she texted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.29,0:18:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said I'd find you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:54.48,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Received Mail\Nfrom: Satone Shichimiya\Nsub: From Sophia\N...is at the Waterfront Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.91,0:18:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, if you are a fake,\Nconfess your duplicity immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.00,0:19:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My question is based on the most\Ncomplex section of the Mabinogion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are the true one, you can answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.64,0:19:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... death!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.31,0:19:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.52,0:19:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not an issue. Sophia \Ntold me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.65,0:19:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the one who should apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.15,0:19:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am mortified that I should ever\N
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.16,0:19:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have questioned you, Dark Flame Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with whom I have walked in this guise\Nfor so many months and years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.16,0:19:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the fact of the matter is that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we didn't end up spending much time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.22,0:19:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's about time,\Nor maybe it's a little late...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.22,0:19:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The timing just never seemed right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.39,0:19:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.10,0:20:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It has to be today or it's meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.02,0:20:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.61,0:20:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your birthday today, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.05,0:20:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept that information top secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because there is such a\Nhigh probability of being hexed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was there for the whole world to see\Nin your former email address!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.29,0:20:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.29,0:20:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.60,0:20:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.97,0:20:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your old one is really worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.52,0:20:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought this would make you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.48,0:20:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.77,0:20:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Schwartz Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.57,0:20:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Schwartz Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.78,0:20:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.28,0:20:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it at the place we visited\Nthe other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bonus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.20,0:20:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is true power of darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to stay the\NWicked Lord Shingan forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.42,0:21:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think you can revive\Nthe Dark Flame Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.89,0:21:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.01,0:21:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you believe the Dark Flame Dragon\Nis alive inside of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.52,0:21:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you become Ghelzonianses someday?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.85,0:21:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can't say for sure about\Nthe Dark Flame Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.03,0:21:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but something could \Nbe sleeping inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.45,0:21:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought that the\Nobvious answer to that was no...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.37,0:21:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it's not so bad to believe\Nthat something is in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.12,0:21:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.25,0:21:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't mean I can conjure up\Nthe flames of darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.46,0:21:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're conjuring them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.71,0:21:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no. This is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.63,0:21:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.47,0:21:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.07,0:22:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Be\NContinued
